
sau chāñd bhī chamkeñge to kyā baat banegī 
tum aa.e to is raat kī auqāt banegī 
un se yahī kah aa.eñ ki ab ham na mileñge 
āḳhir koī taqrīb-e-mulāqāt banegī 
ai nāvak-e-ġham dil meñ hai ik buuñd lahū kī 
kuchh aur to kyā ham se mudārāt banegī 
ye ham se na hogā ki kisī ek ko chāheñ 
ai ishq hamārī na tire saat banegī 
ye kyā hai ki baḌhte chalo baḌhte chalo aage 
jab baiTh ke socheñge to kuchh baat banegī 